               <p>MARY ANN BOTELAR. I live at No. 68, Charlotte-street, Portland Place. I am single. I know the prisoner - I was present when he was married at St. Andrew's, Holborn, on the 14th of October, 1827 - he married 
               <persName id="t18340410-199-victim1289" type="victimName">
                  Mary Ann 
                  Harvey
               <interp inst="t18340410-199-victim1289" type="surname" value="Harvey"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-199-victim1289" type="given" value="Mary Ann"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340410-199-victim1289" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             - I was her bridesmaid - I knew the prisoner before that time, and Mary Ann Harvey also - she is now alive; I saw her to-day - I am positive the prisoner and she were the persons who were then married.</p>
               <p>
            
